    {
      "instruction": "<p>Transfer the <strong>browned chicken</strong> to a<strong> tin foil</strong>-lined baking tray and scrunch the edges of the foil up a little around it</p><p>Tip: This will help to keep the sauce around your chicken!</p><p>Drizzle your <strong>smoky</strong> <strong>BBQ sauce </strong>all over and put the tray in the oven for an initial 10 min</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
